{"tid":1904444,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【孫楊禁賽8年】胡鍚進：不主張把孫楊問題與國家榮辱劃上等號","createTime":"2020-02-29T15:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T09:52:06.000Z","uid":224066,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6fea8ff8387e02671b096165fe9e8185784a10","tid":1904444,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e591f095e00e37651d96655.jpg/RVBocaF4QYeI-ZOSxebZ-R4ksbFrZXb-ScwRLknMES4?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e591f095e00e37651d96655.jpg%2FRVBocaF4QYeI-ZOSxebZ-R4ksbFrZXb-ScwRLknMES4%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=89998f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國著名遊泳運動員孫楊被國際體育仲裁法庭裁定有罪，被重罰禁賽八年，不但恐怕無緣即將舉行的東京奧運，甚至更有可能賠上整個運動員生涯。孫楊的情況引起內地網民強烈反響，紛紛表達支持上訴。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡鍚進亦發文表示支持上訴，但強調要就事論事，「無需讓這種支持變成一種和國家榮譽相聯系的情緒和戰鬥」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ogwxaz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgwxaz7.jpg&h=f1808c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進指，今是孫楊本人及國際泳聯與世界禁藥劑機構的嚴重糾紛，不應視為中國受到的挑戰。孫楊曾經獲得奧運等多項國際大賽的冠軍，為國爭光，「但我不主張把孫楊所遇到的具體問題和國家的榮辱劃等號」。胡鍚進表示，不排除法庭的法官有受到一些西方輿論的影響，對證據的採納也可能有問題，所以支持孫楊要依法維權，「但我依然不主張對該法庭仲裁的複雜性進行簡單的政治解讀」。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進又提到，中國和中國人在國際場合都可能有一些不利因素，「但要看到，中國的經濟社會發展、包括體育事業都在這個大環境裏通過我們的努力取得了長足進步，這證明，其間的一些障礙經過我們努力是能夠突破、化解的」，是故中國應當對對外開放的總體環境保持信心。"},{"pid":"04d9d4dcb3792d60841e10c955865ac0798a5784","tid":1904444,"uid":27416,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"「定性」為condom"},{"pid":"6bc5ea9d4f3d981f718cc511dd4e5e0e3ecf9cac","tid":1904444,"uid":265839,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"逐漸變condom 又得，立即變condom 亦得"},{"pid":"4793201c1222e1b31c9f3b75dc5a59461d4b21c8","tid":1904444,"uid":70313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bc5ea9d4f3d981f718cc511dd4e5e0e3ecf9cac","tid":1904444,"uid":265839,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"逐漸變condom 又得，立即變condom 亦得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7647fb476ef8ae879f11912662dcfca7fb90c9e","tid":1904444,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:54:35.000Z","msg":"風向撚"},{"pid":"df61ff61a8ec4481c8b1830551507d7063570dc7","tid":1904444,"uid":176996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:54:57.000Z","msg":"condom"},{"pid":"926ef125f2fb0ce224ebdf83d8b085d04932922e","tid":1904444,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"割蓆"},{"pid":"b70861cd0f7655fb51b9ad801885e9e80ed21943","tid":1904444,"uid":117422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8fa234514c88474d86debc91317b73f6a11694","tid":1904444,"uid":116554,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"肉撚酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73b5bb5b561d2e0afa4749f24064d9b9aff2c59","tid":1904444,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:01:02.000Z","msg":"你唔畫就唔等於？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2efd65dc9581a7cf396cb43fbbab3f632449386","tid":1904444,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9hj8HacSg8w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9hj8HacSg8w&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXAfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=54d4f634\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9hj8HacSg8w</a><br />\n大家一齊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05632e916703a13b4247f603592107fccb8701db","tid":1904444,"uid":28195,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"鐘南山個女係全中國因為食藥而被國際停賽的中國游泳選手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTsz8u9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTsz8u9.jpg&h=7b858012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a7ca4afad53922e81581fd827cac4fed5bca034","tid":1904444,"uid":49316,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"编者推荐<br />\n孫楊事件牽出中國泳史禁賽第一人：鐘南山女兒<br />\n<br />\n【2020年2月28日】（歐洲希望之聲何梓涵綜合報導）今日（28日）中國泳壇名將孫楊因拒絕藥檢被禁賽8年。隨後網絡爆料，中共衛健委新冠病毒權威專家鐘南山的女兒鐘惟月，是中國游泳史上第一個被查出服用禁藥而被禁賽的運動員。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，鐘南山的女兒鐘惟月，曾就讀美國南加州大學會計專業，後成為游泳運動員。她曾獲得過世界短池游泳錦標賽100米蝶泳冠軍，還打破過短池蝶泳的世界紀錄。 1994年羅馬世錦賽上，因尿檢呈陽性，疑似使用興奮劑，成為中國頂尖游泳選手裡第一個被禁賽的運動員。<br />\n<br />\n當時人民日報的汪大昭評論說，「鐘惟月一看就是吃藥的，說話和長相和男的沒有什麼區別，早就該揪出來了」。<br />\n<br />\n有網友不解，鐘南山作為醫生，對自己女兒的情況應該早有察覺，當然更知道吃禁藥對身體的壞處，不知道他為什麼能容忍此事發生。"},{"pid":"ba52400f28da838543c79aedfa8896d1efc207b1","tid":1904444,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcaf116f5caa54843af8943439c3691e66411395","tid":1904444,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05632e916703a13b4247f603592107fccb8701db","tid":1904444,"uid":28195,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"鐘南山個女係全中國因為食藥而被國際停賽的中國游泳選手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTsz8u9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTsz8u9.jpg&h=7b858012&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"鍾南山不嬲仆街"},{"pid":"5c9949f396ec77befd23e7839ecc7fae291e8fea","tid":1904444,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"條撚樣終於乞食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5168c35059c751df187e68268d56b5e76bba274f","tid":1904444,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"做咩佢啲相成日都拿埋一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8b9b94a75fad99179ef09d165ca09cc92fb9c4","tid":1904444,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"Who's the loser now? Cocksucker Sun."},{"pid":"252c7ce46025c6aa0b682dfc3931e6ff8e8b40c2","tid":1904444,"uid":106321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"條撚樣胡錫進幾時先肯執下個髮型？<br />\n成個乞衣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7702a9ee095047fb1ef634f03115ecd9783895","tid":1904444,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"252c7ce46025c6aa0b682dfc3931e6ff8e8b40c2","tid":1904444,"uid":106321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"條撚樣胡錫進幾時先肯執下個髮型？<br />\n成個乞衣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"中共有名你叫共匪，點會執得正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a903b4ae6ee558bba3626f158c618f6f8a71fc1c","tid":1904444,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05632e916703a13b4247f603592107fccb8701db","tid":1904444,"uid":28195,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"鐘南山個女係全中國因為食藥而被國際停賽的中國游泳選手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTsz8u9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTsz8u9.jpg&h=7b858012&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"現居於美國了"},{"pid":"3fc35df9e47e5a69a843e8cd4508113926b52423","tid":1904444,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"252c7ce46025c6aa0b682dfc3931e6ff8e8b40c2","tid":1904444,"uid":1